@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName monospace
skinparam padding 5

title Workflow 1: Global Project Scope (Macro)

actor User
participant "gptel Context" as Context
participant "LLM Agent" as LLM
participant "investigate_code_tag" as Tool1
database "Project TAGS" as Tags

User -> Context : 1. Injects TAGS file into context
User -> LLM : 2. Prompts about an architectural issue
LLM -> Tool1 : 3. Autonomously queries dependencies
Tool1 -> Tags : 4. Reads exact geometric boundaries
Tool1 --> LLM : 5. Returns lean source code fragment
LLM --> User : 6. Delivers precise answer
@enduml